headline: Rockwell Automation to Present at the 2025 J.P. Morgan Industrials Conference
summary: MILWAUKEE, February 26, 2025--Rockwell Automation, Inc. (NYSE: ROK) SVP and CFO, Christian Rothe, will present at the 2025 J.P. Morgan Industrials Conference on Wednesday, March 12, 2025, in New York.
